                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                此課程依照選課同學之教育，工作背景，主要介紹1)國際級酒店之組織架構及各部門之關聯性2）國際知名品牌的排序，其分級，及設施，服務，佈局之重點3）國際酒店之各部門及整體管理4）經由校外教學，客座講師及課堂討論之安排，讓學生能：1）對全球，包括中國，的旅館現狀及最新發展有所瞭解2）實地觀察，體驗國際水準的觀光旅館前，後台（Front and back of the house)各項設備及所提供之服務3）由一個部門來瞭解各部門乃至整體的互不可缺性。希望由此激發同學對旅館管理的興趣及熱忱，甚或以此為終身事業！

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                Based on students’ educational and work background, the course mainly introduce 1) International standard hotel’s organizational chart and its inter-related relationship 2) International chain hotels’ ranking and the categories, facilities, services offered and future plan of each hotel chain 3) How to manage each department in the hotel and the overall management concept 4) Through field trip, guest speaker, discussion and presentation in the class, we hope the students are able to: 1) have certain understanding on global, including China, hotels’ present situation and future strategy 2) Observe and experience the entire international standard hotel’s facilities and services which include front and back of the house 3) understand the perfect set-up of an international hotel through detailed explanation of one particular department.Hopefully by end of the course, we are able to inspire the interest and love of all students towards hotel management business and make this their life-time career!











                                Material
                            

                                 
                            

                                上課教材
                            

                                 
                            





                                1) Instructor’s note2) Domestic and internationally related publications, journals, to name a few:   2.1) Hotel Management Magazine   2.2) Marketing for Hospitality and Tourism (by Philip Kotler, John Bowen, James Makens)   2.3) Introduction on Hospitality (by John Walker)   2.4) Hospitality Management and Organizational Behavior (by Laurie J.Mullins, Penny Dossor)   2.5) Hotel Management and Operations (by Denny G.Rutherford)   2.7) Global Alliances in Tourism and Hospitality Management (by Dinmitrios Buhalis, John C.Crotts,Roger March)   2.8) The spirit to serve: Marriott’s Way   2.9) 中國酒店管理模式 (黃鑒中，復旦大學出版社）











